divs: Sighting DetailsTraveling home on HWY 7 East in my vehicle.Just happened to look up at the sky to the North.An airplane.I didnt see any port or starboard lighting or flashing anti-collision lights.So I asked my brother sitting next to me, whatdo you think that isIt looked like an oval, featureless, lighted object traveling at a high rate ofspeed. Travelling from the north in a southern direction. Then the entire objectflashed or blinked on and off several times as it flew to the southern horizon.We watched it for about 30 seconds as it dissapeared on the horizon.flashed or blinked all over on and off several times
